.SH NAME
megasas_adp_reset_wait_for_ready \- initiate chip reset and wait for controller to come to ready state
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" megasas_adp_reset_wait_for_ready
.BI "(struct megasas_instance *instance "  ","
.BI "bool do_adp_reset "  ","
.BI "int ocr_context "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "instance" 12
adapter's soft state
.IP "do_adp_reset" 12
If true, do a chip reset
.IP "ocr_context" 12
If called from OCR context this will
be set to 1, else 0
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function initates a chip reset followed by a wait for controller to
transition to ready state.
During this, driver will block all access to PCI config space from userspace
